1
00:00:00,166 --> 00:00:01,216
對不起。
Sorry.

2
00:00:03,116 --> 00:00:05,273
你夏天要幹什麼？
What are you doing over the summer?

3
00:00:07,285 --> 00:00:09,609
我在加油站找了份工作
I have a job pumping gas.

4
00:00:09,954 --> 00:00:12,787
你終於讓最高法院聽你的了，嗯？
You finally got the Supreme Court to hear your case, huh?

5
00:00:15,793 --> 00:00:17,286
你呢？
What about you?

6
00:00:18,629 --> 00:00:19,956
不知道。
I don't know.

7
00:00:22,466 --> 00:00:24,457
你覺得在這更好？
You thought it'd be nicer over here?

8
00:00:26,636 --> 00:00:27,666
嗯
Yeah.

9
00:00:36,979 --> 00:00:38,353
你在幹什麼
What are you doing?

10
00:00:41,483 --> 00:00:44,435
找點什麼送我媽媽生日禮物
I'm looking for something for my mom's birthday.

11
00:00:46,571 --> 00:00:48,028
你的意思是說，萬一有人偶爾在沙灘上丟了
You mean, in case somebody happened to leave...

12
00:00:48,113 --> 00:00:49,938
一個Cuisinart（美國廚具品牌）的東西或者一個鑽石戒指？
a Cuisinart or a diamond ring lying on the beach?

13
00:00:50,324 --> 00:00:53,489
是啊，那就行。必須得是你做的，或者是你找到的東西。
Yeah, that would qualify. It has to be omething either you make or find.

14
00:00:53,577 --> 00:00:56,113
- 她生日是什麼時候？
- 下周。
- When's her birthday?
- Next week.

15
00:01:18,057 --> 00:01:19,550
真美。
That's beautiful.

16
00:01:21,728 --> 00:01:23,386
給你媽媽的。
It's for your mother.

17
00:01:26,065 --> 00:01:27,558
你送給她。
You give it to her.

18
00:01:30,277 --> 00:01:31,307
好
Okay.

19
00:01:35,323 --> 00:01:36,899
在那一定更好。
It must be nicer over there.

20
00:01:39,160 --> 00:01:41,317
過來，切這些。
Here, chop these.

21
00:01:51,129 --> 00:01:54,212
不對，不對，不對。看。你到一邊去。
No, no, no. Watch. Move.

22
00:01:54,798 --> 00:01:56,540
拿著刀……
You hold the knife...

23
00:01:56,634 --> 00:01:58,791
就這麼做。
and you just do that.

24
00:01:59,136 --> 00:02:00,545
很乾淨。我試試
That's neat. Let me try.

25
00:02:00,637 --> 00:02:05,131
不，不。我是個素食者，我可不想你把你的小手指頭切到菜裡去。
No, no. I'm a vegetarian. I don't want pieces of tiny little fingers in my stew.

26
00:02:05,225 --> 00:02:06,552
這。你來攪拌。
Here. You stir.

27
00:02:09,062 --> 00:02:10,852
你在等誰嗎？
Were you expecting someone?

28
00:02:19,446 --> 00:02:20,476
嗨。
Hi.

29
00:02:22,073 --> 00:02:23,400
我是羅娜。
I'm Lorna.

30
00:02:24,659 --> 00:02:26,317
麥克邀請了我。
Michael invited me.

31
00:02:27,662 --> 00:02:29,487
好吧，進來吧
Well, come in.

32
00:02:35,419 --> 00:02:36,912
你朋友在這
Your friend's here.

33
00:02:38,422 --> 00:02:39,452
嗨
Hi.

34
00:02:42,467 --> 00:02:44,257
- 嗨。
- 我可以幫忙麼？
- Hi.
- Can I help?

35
00:02:44,635 --> 00:02:46,959
不用，不用，沒關係。謝謝。
No. No, it's okay. Thank you.

36
00:02:47,471 --> 00:02:48,964
你切到手指了。
You cut your finger.

37
00:02:49,056 --> 00:02:50,086
是啊
Yeah.

38
00:02:50,599 --> 00:02:52,424
這是你女朋友？
Is this your girlfriend?

39
00:02:52,768 --> 00:02:54,593
嗨，我是史蒂芬。
Hi, I'm Stephen.

40
00:02:57,606 --> 00:03:00,558
真好吃，寶貝。完全超出你的水平
That was delicious, babe.You outdid yourself.

41
00:03:00,650 --> 00:03:03,982
為我自己的安格魯-撒克遜教徒準備的朝聖食物。
This pilgrim food for my very own WASP.

42
00:03:04,570 --> 00:03:06,312
但是你得原諒我，親愛的
But you must forgive me, my darling.

43
00:03:06,405 --> 00:03:08,894
我沒法做出這種果凍模具
I couldn't get myself to make one of those Jell-O molds.

44
00:03:10,659 --> 00:03:12,401
這次就原諒你了
You're forgiven this time.

45
00:03:12,494 --> 00:03:14,983
現在，（法語）
And now, for the pi鎗e de r閟istance.

46
00:03:15,247 --> 00:03:18,412
- 我來，爸爸
- 你被逮捕了
- Let me, Dad.
- You're under arrest.

47
00:03:28,174 --> 00:03:30,414
看看，你弄得肚臍那到處都是
Look at this.You got it all over your bellybutton.

48
00:03:30,510 --> 00:03:32,168
看看
Look at that.

49
00:03:32,637 --> 00:03:36,300
哦天哪。我老得都能把這房子弄著火。
Oh, God. I'm old enough to set the house on fire.

50
00:03:59,578 --> 00:04:02,494
抱歉，我以為你媽媽叫辛西婭。
I'm sorry, I thought your mother's name was Cynthia.

51
00:04:02,831 --> 00:04:04,822
過生日的時候我們都叫山姆
On birthdays, we're all Sam.

52
00:04:05,125 --> 00:04:06,534
這是我們家小小的傳統……
It's a little family tradition...

53
00:04:06,626 --> 00:04:10,289
是因為我1968年那次超棒的用迷幻劑的經歷
resulting from a particularly good LSD trip I took in 1968.

54
00:04:13,799 --> 00:04:15,126
再來點酒？
More wine?

55
00:04:16,677 --> 00:04:19,510
- 你能讓我歇會麼？
- 在歐洲，小孩子就能喝酒。
- Would you give me a break?
- In Europe, kids drink wine.

56
00:04:19,596 --> 00:04:23,924
在我給「匿名酗酒者（美國一家幫助戒酒的機構）」打電話（指喝醉）之前，把給你媽媽的禮物拿來。
Get your mother her present before I call Alcoholics Anonymous.

57
00:04:33,233 --> 00:04:34,263
謝謝
Thanks.

58
00:04:39,948 --> 00:04:42,864
這就是我想要的
It's just what I wanted.

59
00:04:42,951 --> 00:04:45,275
- 真的？
- 千真萬確
- Really?
- Absolutely.

60
00:04:49,624 --> 00:04:51,414
那是什麼，蝴蝶？
What is that, a butterfly?

61
00:04:51,500 --> 00:04:53,787
不是，是個鯨魚，當做禮物了
No, it's a whale of a present.

62
00:05:01,300 --> 00:05:03,042
- 謝謝
- 我會彈奏它的
- Thanks.- I'll play it for you sometime.

63
00:05:04,011 --> 00:05:06,500
這是羅娜的禮物
This is from Lorna.

64
00:05:14,354 --> 00:05:16,012
真美
That's beautiful.

65
00:05:16,939 --> 00:05:18,597
謝謝你，羅娜
Thank you, Lorna.

66
00:05:21,527 --> 00:05:23,684
我的禮物，等會給你
Mine, you get later.

67
00:05:24,196 --> 00:05:25,357
你保證
You bet.

68
00:05:26,365 --> 00:05:27,692
沒問題
On your feet!

69
00:05:27,949 --> 00:05:29,276
我來幫忙。
Let me help.

70
00:05:31,536 --> 00:05:33,029
我喜歡她。
I like her.

71
00:05:33,121 --> 00:05:34,199
嗯？
Yeah?

72
00:05:34,289 --> 00:05:36,613
- 我也喜歡她。
- 我知道
- I like her, too.- I know.

73
00:06:32,299 --> 00:06:34,586
你確定這是菲利普斯家的孩子？
You sure this is the Phillips' kid?

74
00:06:34,843 --> 00:06:37,415
你在醫院沒被掉包吧，嗯？
They didn't switch you at the hospital,or anything, did they?

75
00:07:35,773 --> 00:07:38,808
你知道，我不敢想像他們有多不可理喻。
You know, I can't believe how incredible they are.

76
00:07:39,151 --> 00:07:44,310
你知道如果我給我媽媽一個貝殼當做生日禮物，她會怎麼做？
Do you know what my mother would do if I gave her a shell for her birthday?

77
00:07:44,739 --> 00:07:46,397
沒關係吧
They're okay.

78
00:07:47,325 --> 00:07:50,158
那就是你，害怕承認自己
That's you all over,afraid to commit yourself.

79
00:07:51,078 --> 00:07:52,903
我以為這就是我
I thought it was just me.

80
00:07:57,167 --> 00:07:58,957
和你在一起我很開心
I'm very happy with you.

81
00:08:01,588 --> 00:08:03,828
我也是
I'm very happy with you, too.

82
00:09:02,100 --> 00:09:04,174
沒關係，我想這樣
It's okay, I want to.

83
00:09:56,441 --> 00:09:58,930
- 你沒去上廚藝課
- 你注意到了。
- You weren't in cooking.
- You noticed.

84
00:09:59,444 --> 00:10:01,435
- 你去哪了？
- 我翹課了
- Where were you?- I cut.

85
00:10:03,156 --> 00:10:05,527
- 為什麼？
- 我不想見你。
- Why?- I didn't want to see you.

86
00:10:28,345 --> 00:10:31,344
曼菲爾德，我能和你說幾句話麼
Manfield, could I talk to you for a minute?

87
00:10:36,352 --> 00:10:39,020
你沒必要這麼緊張。就算你做了錯事……
You don't have to look so anxious.If you've done something wrong...

88
00:10:39,105 --> 00:10:42,140
我也不知道。我只是想知道你對大學的計劃。
I don't know about it. I just want to talk to you about your college plans.

89
00:10:42,233 --> 00:10:46,229
我想休息一年，也許去歐洲旅行，聽聽音樂。
I was thinking of taking a year off, maybe traveling to Europe, listening to music.

90
00:10:46,320 --> 00:10:49,818
我不能要求你做什麼，但是我覺得你應該申請大學
I can't tell you what to do, but I think you ought to make an application, anyway.

91
00:10:49,906 --> 00:10:51,862
你可以推遲入學的
You can always postpone entry.

92
00:10:51,949 --> 00:10:54,320
我想讓你考慮考慮申請朱利亞德（紐約一所藝術學院）
I'd like you to consider applying to Juilliard.

93
00:10:54,410 --> 00:10:55,951
提前錄取
Early admission.

94
00:10:59,790 --> 00:11:03,703
我看了你成績的檔案，被錄取應該沒問題
I looked at your academic records.You should have no trouble getting in.

95
00:11:04,086 --> 00:11:05,283
不過，剩下的呢？
Where's the rest of it, by the way?

96
00:11:05,379 --> 00:11:07,417
你的檔案裡沒有原先的學校的。
There's nothing in your file from your old school.

97
00:11:09,132 --> 00:11:11,289
我們搬家的時候弄丟了。
It was lost when we moved.

98
00:11:12,634 --> 00:11:14,127
找回來的時候，我想看看。
When it comes through, I'd like to see it.

99
00:11:15,387 --> 00:11:17,378
同時，你看看這個。
In the meantime, you look at that.

100
00:11:22,477 --> 00:11:24,598
我會樂意給你寫推薦信的。
I'd be happy to write you a letter of recommendation.

101
00:11:25,313 --> 00:11:26,556
謝謝
Thank you.

102
00:11:29,651 --> 00:11:32,057
看完之後還給我
Get back to me when you've looked at it.

103
00:12:37,587 --> 00:12:39,578
你不和我說話
You wouldn't talk to me.

104
00:12:42,090 --> 00:12:43,417
現在，起床
Now, get up.

105
00:12:43,800 --> 00:12:46,289
下樓，從後門出去
Go down the stairs and out the back door.

106
00:12:46,803 --> 00:12:48,296
悄悄的
Be quiet.

107
00:12:58,147 --> 00:12:59,972
我就在你後面。
I'll be right behind you.

108
00:13:12,701 --> 00:13:14,359
我光著腳呢
I'm barefoot.

109
00:13:46,857 --> 00:13:48,018
坐下
Sit down.

110
00:13:56,991 --> 00:13:58,532
我在幹嘛？
What am I doing?

111
00:14:02,371 --> 00:14:04,409
我就是想和你說話。
I just wanted to talk to you.

112
00:14:06,667 --> 00:14:08,991
你那天在學校不聽我講。
You wouldn't listen, the other day at school.

113
00:14:15,174 --> 00:14:19,751
我那天晚上沒和你在一起，不是因為我不想。
I couldn't stay with you that night. Not because I didn't want to.

114
00:14:29,563 --> 00:14:31,887
如果你想回去，對我來說沒什麼。
If you want to go back, it's fine with me.

115
00:14:33,774 --> 00:14:35,979
- 你是個笨蛋。
- 不。
- You're a bully.- No.

116
00:14:39,571 --> 00:14:41,028
我說了謊。
I'm a liar.

117
00:14:44,576 --> 00:14:46,234
我真名不是麥克
My name isn't Michael.

118
00:14:48,705 --> 00:14:49,818
是丹尼。
It's Danny.

119
00:14:51,332 --> 00:14:55,079
我父母是阿瑟和安妮·波普
My parents are Arthur and Annie Pope.

120
00:14:57,504 --> 00:15:01,832
1971年他們因為讓汽油彈實驗室爆炸，和聯邦調查局惹上了麻煩
They're in trouble with the FBl for blowing up a napalm lab in 1971.

121
00:15:01,925 --> 00:15:03,797
有一個人差點就死了
There was a man who was almost killed.

122
00:15:03,885 --> 00:15:05,793
那是個看門人，當時不該在那的
A janitor,abcwho wasn't supposed to be there.

123
00:15:05,887 --> 00:15:08,803
我們在所有生日蛋糕上都寫「山姆」
We put "Sam" on the birthday cakes, on all the birthday cakes...

124
00:15:09,682 --> 00:15:12,136
是因為每到一個地方，我們就換新名字
because we change our names every time we move.

125
00:15:15,104 --> 00:15:18,269
從我兩歲起，就一直這樣了
I've been doing this since I was two.

126
00:15:19,315 --> 00:15:21,140
我不知道別的辦法。
I don't know any other way.

127
00:15:21,817 --> 00:15:25,184
我只是想告訴你我很抱歉
I just wanted to tell you that I was sorry.

128
00:15:28,240 --> 00:15:31,572
我想解釋我為什麼說不了太多事
I wanted to explain why I can't talk about a lot of things.

129
00:15:32,161 --> 00:15:35,778
比如大學。我不能去上大學。我不能離開他們。
Like college. I can't go to college.I can't leave them.

130
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:41,325
我還想告訴你……
And I wanted to tell you...

131
00:15:42,503 --> 00:15:44,209
我為什麼不能和你在一起。
why I couldn't be with you.

132
00:15:45,214 --> 00:15:48,047
不能讓你不知道。我不想對你說謊。
Not without your knowing.I didn't want to lie to you.

133
00:15:50,010 --> 00:15:53,757
現在我沒權利和你說這些的
Now, I have no right in telling this to you.

134
00:15:53,847 --> 00:15:56,680
對你，對他們，都很危險。
It's dangerous for you,and it's dangerous for them.

135
00:15:58,852 --> 00:16:01,057
對不起，我只是控制不住自己
I'm sorry. I just couldn't stop myself.

136
00:16:01,561 --> 00:16:05,142
你想做什麼都可以做，你可以告訴你爸爸。我不介意
You can do what you want to. You can tell your dad anything. I don't care.

137
00:16:06,149 --> 00:16:07,974
我只是想要你知道
I just needed you to know.

138
00:16:09,652 --> 00:16:11,976
我不知道我在做什麼
I don't know what I'm doing.

139
00:16:14,824 --> 00:16:16,067
我愛你
And I love you.

140
00:16:20,663 --> 00:16:21,990
我愛你
I love you.

141
00:16:53,817 --> 00:16:55,310
那我要叫你什麼？
What do I call you?

142
00:16:55,402 --> 00:16:58,437
麥克。什麼都不用變
Michael. Nothing changes.

143
00:16:59,364 --> 00:17:01,688
他們真的不想讓你上大學麼？
They really don't want you to go to school, huh?

144
00:17:04,285 --> 00:17:06,110
我們還沒有談
We haven't talked about it.

145
00:17:06,955 --> 00:17:08,661
- 我不能問他們
- 為什麼不？
- I can't ask them.- Why not?

146
00:17:10,290 --> 00:17:12,958
那就意味著拆散整個家庭，我再也見不到他們。
It would mean breaking up the family,not seeing them again.

147
00:17:14,419 --> 00:17:16,375
他們除了我們，什麼都沒有
They don't have anything else.

148
00:17:17,881 --> 00:17:22,874
我不能相信他們會要求你耗費自己的生命去陪著他們
I can't believe that they'd want you to give up your whole life to stay with them.

149
00:17:23,469 --> 00:17:25,793
和他們談。他們會理解的。
Talk to them. They'll understand.

150
00:17:30,433 --> 00:17:32,590
你有很多秘密，不是麼
You have a lot of secrets, don't you?

151
00:17:34,354 --> 00:17:36,144
現在你又多了一個。
Now you have another one.

152
00:18:17,809 --> 00:18:19,302
去和羅娜約會了？
Been to see Lorna?

153
00:18:29,362 --> 00:18:30,855
我喜歡她。
I like that one.

154
00:18:31,322 --> 00:18:32,980
她很活潑
She's full of beans.

155
00:18:35,701 --> 00:18:37,526
你真心喜歡她，不是麼
You really like her, don't you?

156
00:18:38,870 --> 00:18:41,110
聰明的人總是最好的
The smart ones are always the best.

157
00:18:43,374 --> 00:18:45,080
你和她睡了麼？
Are you sleeping with her?

158
00:18:46,794 --> 00:18:48,868
- 嗯。
- 好。
- Yeah.
- Okay.

159
00:18:50,548 --> 00:18:53,298
快去，睡覺去。明天還要上學。
Go ahead, hit the sack.You got school tomorrow.

160
00:20:02,654 --> 00:20:04,894
你在停止專業鋼琴之後
How long have you been playing violin...

161
00:20:04,990 --> 00:20:08,155
演奏了多久小提琴？
after you stopped playing seriously piano?

162
00:20:08,826 --> 00:20:10,105
大概五年
About five years.

163
00:20:10,202 --> 00:20:11,992
什麼時候來美國的？
When did you come to the States?

164
00:20:12,830 --> 00:20:14,109
1980年
In 1980.

165
00:20:14,206 --> 00:20:16,280
好的，非常感謝
All right. Thank you very much.

166
00:20:16,875 --> 00:20:19,874
曼菲爾德先生，我們準備好面試你了。
Mr. Manfield. We're ready for you now.

167
00:22:51,348 --> 00:22:53,802
你說你和誰學的？
Who did you say you studied with?

168
00:22:55,435 --> 00:22:56,976
愛德華·菲利普斯
Edward Phillips.

169
00:22:57,061 --> 00:22:59,467
- 在哪？
- 沃特福德。
- Where was this?- Waterford.

170
