because it is your child who is pulling the triggers, setting the bombs.

344
00:38:30,527 --> 00:38:32,518
我沒殺任何人
I didn't kill anybody.

345
00:38:35,198 --> 00:38:38,861
我不是來為自己辯護或是談政治的
I didn't come here to defend myself or to talk politics.

346
00:38:40,035 --> 00:38:44,779
如果你不相信我當時那麼做是出於良心要結束戰爭
If you don't believe by now that what I did was an act of conscience to stop the war...

347
00:38:45,207 --> 00:38:48,290
那我說什麼你都不會明白
then there's nothing I can say to you that's going to make you understand.

348
00:38:48,377 --> 00:38:50,368
一個人失明，還殘疾了
A man was blinded and paralyzed.

349
00:38:50,462 --> 00:38:52,204
他本不該在那的。
He wasn't supposed to be there.

350
00:38:56,718 --> 00:38:58,175
你不覺得，有些時候
Don't you think there have been times...

351
00:38:58,261 --> 00:39:01,177
我寧願讓自己失明，讓自己殘疾，來挽回這一切麼？
that I would have blinded and paralyzed myself to take that back?

352
00:39:01,471 --> 00:39:03,047
那都是阿瑟的影響。
It's all Arthur's influence.

353
00:39:03,140 --> 00:39:04,798
不，爸爸，不是
No, Dad, it isn't.

354
00:39:05,684 --> 00:39:07,058
是我的主意。
It was my idea.

355
00:39:07,644 --> 00:39:10,133
我活在我自己的選擇帶來的後果中
I'm living with the consequences of my own choice.

356
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:12,102
- 我不信。
- 那是你的問題
- I don't believe it.- Well, that's your problem.

357
00:39:12,190 --> 00:39:13,766
你媽媽和我……
Your mother and me...

358
00:39:15,026 --> 00:39:16,567
你為我們考慮過麼？
Do you think about us?

359
00:39:23,491 --> 00:39:26,027
- 你非得這麼問麼
- 對。
- Do you really have to ask that?- Yes.

360
00:39:31,707 --> 00:39:34,196
上一次我記得你對我說
The last thing I remember you saying to me...

361
00:39:35,628 --> 00:39:38,034
我是個帝國主義的蠢豬
was that I was an imperialist pig...

362
00:39:38,297 --> 00:39:43,290
一個人為了戰爭，貧窮和種族主義承擔責任
personally responsible for the war, the spread of poverty, racism.

363
00:39:44,553 --> 00:39:46,176
- 我還年輕
- 是
- I was young.- Yes.

364
00:39:49,890 --> 00:39:51,715
你還年輕
You were young.

365
00:39:53,227 --> 00:39:54,554
有才華
And talented.

366
00:39:56,563 --> 00:39:57,641
美麗
And beautiful.

367
00:39:58,982 --> 00:40:00,807
那麼充滿了愛
And so full of love.

368
00:40:03,528 --> 00:40:06,860
上帝啊，安妮。你為什麼把它們都拋棄了？
My God, Annie.Why did you throw it all away?

369
00:40:13,161 --> 00:40:16,326
你媽媽很想你。還有丹尼
Your mother misses you terribly. And Danny.

370
00:40:21,044 --> 00:40:22,702
你會收留他麼，爸爸
Will you take him, Dad?

371
00:40:25,381 --> 00:40:27,004
他想學音樂
He wants to study music.

372
00:40:27,883 --> 00:40:29,376
他很好
He's good.

373
00:40:29,884 --> 00:40:31,590
他們想讓他去朱利亞德
They want him at Juilliard.

374
00:40:33,721 --> 00:40:35,629
就像他們當時想讓你一樣
Just like they wanted you.

375
00:40:39,060 --> 00:40:41,466
你還有那個用來練習的板？
Do you still have that practice board?

376
00:40:42,730 --> 00:40:46,228
一直到現在。丹尼就是在那上面學會彈琴。
So far. Danny learned to play piano on it.

377
00:40:48,068 --> 00:40:49,726
你教他的？
So you taught him?

378
00:40:53,322 --> 00:40:56,321
不覺得這有點諷刺麼？
There's some irony in this, don't you think?

379
00:40:58,035 --> 00:40:59,492
你現在在這
Here you are...

380
00:41:00,204 --> 00:41:02,528
求我把丹尼帶到
asking me to take Danny...

381
00:41:03,373 --> 00:41:07,583
你曾經唯恐避之不及的人生裡
into a life that you ran from like a shot out of hell.

382
00:41:10,213 --> 00:41:11,919
他真的想要麼？
Is this what he wants?

383
00:41:12,006 --> 00:41:13,499
我覺得是
I think so.

384
00:41:13,883 --> 00:41:16,882
他沒告訴我就自己去了面試
He got himself an audition without telling me.

385
00:41:19,679 --> 00:41:23,342
他會需要錢和照顧他的人
He'll need money, and people to care for him.

386
00:41:24,559 --> 00:41:26,799
你不覺得你要的太多了麼？
Don't you think this is too much to ask?

387
00:41:27,979 --> 00:41:29,804
我幾乎不認識這男孩
I hardly know the boy.

388
00:41:31,899 --> 00:41:33,392
如果我們收留了他
If we take him...

389
00:41:36,237 --> 00:41:39,936
那我們去哪都會有聯邦調查局的人跟著
there'd be FBl agents following us everywhere we go.

390
00:41:41,282 --> 00:41:42,656
你就再也見不到他
You'd never be able to see him.

391
00:41:44,702 --> 00:41:46,360
我們太老了，不能這麼做了
We're too old for this.

392
00:41:48,164 --> 00:41:52,030
嗯，我覺得我要的太多了
Yeah, I think it's too much to ask.

393
00:41:58,798 --> 00:42:00,456
我還有一個兒子
I have another son.

394
00:42:01,175 --> 00:42:03,499
他十歲。叫哈利。
He's 10. Harry.

395
00:42:05,512 --> 00:42:07,337
我在新聞上聽說了
I heard about it on the news.

396
00:42:09,349 --> 00:42:11,007
我打算
I plan to turn myself in...

397
00:42:11,101 --> 00:42:14,931
在他再也不需要我的時候就去自首，在他足夠大的時候
when he doesn't need me anymore.When he's old enough.

398
00:42:15,689 --> 00:42:17,016
阿瑟呢？
And Arthur?

399
00:42:17,524 --> 00:42:19,100
我不能為他說話
I can't speak for him.

400
00:42:23,111 --> 00:42:24,936
請你考慮考慮
Please think about this.

401
00:42:32,871 --> 00:42:34,280
我該走了
I should go.

402
00:42:37,333 --> 00:42:38,363
安妮。
Annie.

403
00:42:41,796 --> 00:42:43,502
他可以來我們家
He can come to us.

404
00:42:59,478 --> 00:43:02,228
請您告訴媽媽，我愛她
Please, tell Mom that I love her.

405
00:43:04,149 --> 00:43:06,389
我經常想你倆
And I've thought about you both so often.

406
00:43:07,777 --> 00:43:09,768
我把你叫出來。
I've called out to you.

407
00:43:12,406 --> 00:43:15,738
對不起我給你們帶來這麼多痛苦
I'm sorry that I've caused you so much pain.

408
00:43:20,497 --> 00:43:23,165
我猜我要知道這是什麼感覺了
I guess I'm about to see what it feels like.

409
00:43:28,587 --> 00:43:29,784
我愛你，爸爸
I love you, Dad.

410
00:44:06,163 --> 00:44:07,988
我去見了我父親
I saw my father.

411
00:44:10,000 --> 00:44:11,161
你什麼？
You what?

412
00:44:11,668 --> 00:44:13,493
我見了唐納德
I saw Donald.

413
00:44:15,671 --> 00:44:18,670
你就那麼走進他辦公室坐在他桌邊？
You just walked into his office and sat down at his desk?

414
00:44:18,883 --> 00:44:19,913
沒有
No.

415
00:44:20,050 --> 00:44:23,667
我在「小鍋」和他吃了午飯
I had lunch with him at La Petite Marmite.

416
00:44:24,805 --> 00:44:26,002
幹什麼？
What for?

417
00:44:27,182 --> 00:44:29,173
想看看他要不要收留丹尼.
To see if he'd take Danny.

418
00:44:30,018 --> 00:44:31,676
收留丹尼？
Take Danny?

419
00:44:32,187 --> 00:44:34,143
這樣他就可以上大學了
So he can go to college.

420
00:44:35,981 --> 00:44:37,308
你開玩笑吧
You're kidding.

421
00:44:38,567 --> 00:44:40,060
他說他會的
He said he would.

422
00:44:40,902 --> 00:44:42,560
他說他會？
He said he would?

423
00:44:43,738 --> 00:44:45,943
你知不知道會發生什麼？
You know what could have happened?

424
00:44:47,992 --> 00:44:50,149
菲利普斯要你這麼做的？
Did Phillips put you up to this?

425
00:44:50,286 --> 00:44:52,657
沒人要求我這麼做
Nobody put me up to this.

426
00:44:53,915 --> 00:44:56,914
和菲利普斯無關。這是為了丹尼。
It's not about Phillips. It's about Danny.

427
00:44:57,250 --> 00:45:01,198
他想去。他申請了，去了面試。
He wants to go. He applied.He went to an audition.

428
00:45:01,296 --> 00:45:04,165
- 他他媽的去哪了？
- 朱利亞德
- He went fucking where?- Juilliard.

429
00:45:06,676 --> 00:45:08,418
我不相信我的耳朵。
I don't believe my ears.

430
00:45:08,511 --> 00:45:10,502
就給他一次機會吧。
Just give him a chance.

431
00:45:11,055 --> 00:45:14,138
我要給黛博拉打電話，看看她能不能假造些檔案
I'm going to call Deborah and see if she can make him up some records.

432
00:45:14,225 --> 00:45:15,422
為什麼？
Why?

433
00:45:15,517 --> 00:45:18,185
因為菲力普斯給我填在申請表上的學校打了電話Because Phillips called the school I put on the registration form...

434
00:45:18,270 --> 00:45:20,391
然後他們告訴他沒有叫麥克·曼菲爾德的人
and they told him there was no Michael Manfield.

435
00:45:20,521 --> 00:45:22,512
會沒事的。
It's going to be okay.

436
00:45:22,732 --> 00:45:25,221
他可以及時做好檔案的。阿瑟！
He can get records made up in time. Artie!

437
00:45:28,737 --> 00:45:30,977
我們要搬了，孩子們
We're moving base camp, kids.

438
00:45:32,157 --> 00:45:33,982
再呆幾天，我們就走。
We have a few days, and we're gone.

439
00:45:34,493 --> 00:45:35,986
把蹤跡都銷毀掉。
Cover your tracks.

440
00:45:36,453 --> 00:45:37,780
聽見沒？
You hear me?

441
00:45:39,289 --> 00:45:41,161
你有想告訴我的事麼？
You have anything you want to tell me?

442
00:45:41,623 --> 00:45:42,736
沒有。
No.

443
00:45:42,833 --> 00:45:43,946
好。
Good.

444
00:46:02,560 --> 00:46:04,385
我爸爸想要搬走。
My father wants to move on.

445
00:46:10,567 --> 00:46:11,680
為什麼？
Why?

446
00:46:12,819 --> 00:46:14,525
他有眼見。
He gets a sense.

447
00:46:17,239 --> 00:46:18,400
就那樣？
Just like that?

448
00:46:19,158 --> 00:46:20,651
就那樣。
Just like that.

449
00:46:24,163 --> 00:46:25,324
什麼時候？
When?

450
00:46:26,414 --> 00:46:27,492
隨時。
Anytime.

451
00:46:28,583 --> 00:46:30,408
你就那麼消失了？
You'll just disappear?

452
00:46:38,175 --> 00:46:39,668
那我們怎麼辦？
What about us?

453
00:46:42,804 --> 00:46:45,175
- 他們需要我。
- 我需要你！
- They need me.- I need you!

454
00:46:47,267 --> 00:46:49,009
你沒和他們談？
You didn't talk to them?

455
00:46:52,813 --> 00:46:56,227
你不能一直逃離你沒有責任的事
You can't keep running from something you had nothing to do with.

456
00:46:56,566 --> 00:46:58,723
你應該有你自己的機會
You deserve your own chance.

457
00:47:13,164 --> 00:47:15,570
- 我想和你談談
- 沒什麼可談的
- I want to talk to you.- There's nothing to talk about.

458
00:47:15,667 --> 00:47:17,076
菲利普斯知道的太多了
Phillips knows too much.

459
00:47:17,168 --> 00:47:19,492
你在讓你的情感影響你的判斷。
You were letting your feelings affect your judgment.

460
00:47:19,754 --> 00:47:21,745
而且，這就是上學
Besides, it's academic.

461
00:47:34,058 --> 00:47:35,599
沒人會說的
Nobody will talk.

462
00:47:36,102 --> 00:47:37,263
你不知道。
You don't know that.

463
00:47:38,521 --> 00:47:41,189
他們能抓的都會抓。
They're going to try to pick up everyone they can now.

464
00:47:43,442 --> 00:47:44,721
我們在這的日子到頭了。
We're finished here.

465
00:47:53,034 --> 00:47:55,570
- 我們可以慢慢收手的，不是麼？
- 我們必須走了
- We can close up shop slowly, can't we?- We'll have to.

466
00:47:55,828 --> 00:47:58,496
不然就會引起注意
Otherwise we'll attract attention.

467
00:47:59,414 --> 00:48:01,868
大家都去上班和上學，等接下來的通知
Everybody goes to work and school until further notice.

468
00:48:01,959 --> 00:48:05,161
如果有問題我們就在80號公路附近的野餐區見面
If there's a problem,will meet at the picnic area near Route 80.

469
00:48:05,253 --> 00:48:08,667
還沒有理由覺得他們在追捕我們，所以冷靜
There's no reason to think they're onto us yet, so stay calm.

470
00:48:29,692 --> 00:48:32,691
- 爸爸，我能和你說一會話麼？
- 現在不行。
- Dad, can I talk to you a minute?- Not now.

471
00:48:39,325 --> 00:48:41,233
我想留下。
I was thinking about staying.

472
00:48:41,452 --> 00:48:44,238
- 你不得去上課麼？
- 還有半個小時
- Don't you have school?- In half an hour.

473
00:49:01,388 --> 00:49:02,501
我想留下。
I want to stay.

474
00:49:03,931 --> 00:49:05,092
留下？
Stay?

475
00:49:07,100 --> 00:49:09,221
你覺得現在是討論這個問題的時候麼
Do you think this is a good time to discuss this?

476
00:49:10,520 --> 00:49:12,926
我們現在不能說。我們遇到麻煩了。
We can't talk now. We're in trouble here.

477
00:49:14,274 --> 00:49:15,731
我告訴你了！
I taught you!

478
00:49:16,151 --> 00:49:18,640
我告訴你了！我們不能打破我們之間的聯繫
I taught you! We cannot break rank.

479
00:49:19,279 --> 00:49:21,519
一個集體的能力是由它最弱的一環決定的
A unit is only as good as its weakest link.

480
00:49:21,614 --> 00:49:22,811
我們是一個集體！
We're a unit!

481
00:49:25,158 --> 00:49:27,647
這些都是我教你的，不記得了麼？
I taught you all of this,don't you remember that?

482
00:49:29,746 --> 00:49:31,322
我不想聽你
I don't want to hear you talking about this...

483
00:49:31,414 --> 00:49:33,370
在你媽媽或者你弟弟面前說這些，聽見沒有？
in front of your mother or your brother, do you hear me?

484
00:49:33,458 --> 00:49:34,951
我說，聽見沒有？
I said, do you hear me?

485
00:49:37,211 --> 00:49:39,083
這回說完了沒？
Are we finished talking about this now?

486
00:49:46,844 --> 00:49:47,874
泰勒女士
Mrs. Taylor.

487
00:49:49,514 --> 00:49:51,386
把所有東西都拿出來，穿上袍子就行
Just remove everything and put on the gown.

488
00:49:51,474 --> 00:49:53,180
幾分鐘內就可以見醫生了
The doctor will see you in a few minutes.

489
00:49:55,102 --> 00:49:58,350
好的。我馬上就回來給你稱體重
All right. I'll be right back to weigh you.

490
00:49:59,023 --> 00:50:01,180
能幫我拉拉鏈麼，親愛的？
Could you help me with this zipper, dear?

491
00:50:03,610 --> 00:50:06,230
你知道昨晚伊利莎白·鮑威爾怎麼了麼？
Did you hear what happened to Elizabeth Powell last night?

492
00:50:06,363 --> 00:50:07,393
不知道
No, I didn't.

493
00:50:07,781 --> 00:50:09,938
聯邦調查局找她了
The FBl came to see her.

494
00:50:10,783 --> 00:50:13,023
搶銀行，還殺死了警察的那次
The car that was used in that bank robbery...

495
00:50:13,619 --> 00:50:15,160
他們用的車
where they killed those policemen...

496
00:50:15,245 --> 00:50:17,734
是用她的信用卡租的
it was rented with her credit card.

497
00:50:18,373 --> 00:50:19,830
你相信麼？
Can you believe it?

498
00:50:20,333 --> 00:50:24,329
他們怎麼能拿到她的卡？她自己都從來不用。
How could they have got hold of her card? She never even uses it herself.

499
00:50:24,504 --> 00:50:28,630
這就是為什麼她沒注意到卡不見了
That's how come she didn't notice it was gone.

500
00:50:29,717 --> 00:50:31,708
那些人是一幫惡棍，泰勒女士
Those people are crooks, Mrs. Taylor.

501
00:50:31,802 --> 00:50:34,042
他們很有可能就是從通訊錄裡查出她的電話
They probably just took her name out of the phone book...

502
00:50:34,137 --> 00:50:35,416
然後假造了一張卡。
and made up a false card.

503
00:50:35,889 --> 00:50:37,679
能想像這多背運麼？
Can you imagine the bad luck?

504
00:50:47,191 --> 00:50:50,356
請找保羅·曼菲爾德先生。我是他妻子。
Paul Manfield, please. His wife.

505
00:50:53,696 --> 00:50:55,237
我們很著急。
We're in a hurry.

506
00:50:55,365 --> 00:50:59,147
格斯從我一個病人那偷了信用卡。他用它來租車。
Gus took plastic from one of my patients.He used it to rent the car.

507
00:51:10,212 --> 00:51:13,081
真的？我要去抽根煙
Frankie? I'm going out for a smoke.

